<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RecipeScout</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .jumbotron {
            background-image: url('https://source.unsplash.com/random/1920x1080/?food,cooking');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .jumbotron h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .jumbotron p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .feature {
            padding: 3rem 0;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #ffc107;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h1>RECIPE SCOUT</h1>
            <p class="lead">Discover and create recipes based on the ingredients you have.</p>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Register</a>
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">Login</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>About RecipeScout</h2>
                <p>RecipeScout is a revolutionary platform that helps you discover and create delicious recipes based on the ingredients you have at home. Say goodbye to food waste and hello to culinary adventures!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/random/600x400/?kitchen" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Kitchen">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-dark py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-utensils feature-icon"></i>
                        <h3>Recipe Discovery</h3>
                        <p>Enter the ingredients you have, and RecipeScout will suggest delicious recipes you can make with them.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-book-open feature-icon"></i>
                        <h3>Recipe Creation</h3>
                        <p>Can't find the perfect recipe? Use our intuitive recipe creator to craft your own culinary masterpiece.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-bookmark feature-icon"></i>
                        <h3>Favorites and Meal Planning</h3>
                        <p>Save your favorite recipes and plan your meals with our convenient meal planning feature.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
